<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../public/index.css">
  <title>Recipes</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-4">Recipes! 🥘 🍲 🧆 🍙 🥗 🌯 🍕 🍔 🥞 🌮 </h1>
      <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="container" >
      <h3>Post a recipe</h3>
      <form action="/add-recipe" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="user-name">User name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="user-name" name="user-name" value=<%= user.id %> />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="recipe-name">Recipe Title</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="recipe-name" name="recipe-name" placeholder="eg.. nanas chicken stew" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="recipe-time">Time</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="recipe-time" name='recipe-time'  placeholder="eg.. 45 mins" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="recipe-details">Recipe details</label>
          <textarea class="form-control" id="recipe-details" name="recipe-details" rows="3" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-2" value="Submit" />
      </form>
      <a href="/logout" method="GET">Log out</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Crispy roast potatoes</h5>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">40 mins</h6>
        <p class="card-text">Preheat oven to 450f, Peel potatoes, boil pan of water, 1tsp on baking soda, 1tsp of table
          salt,
          boil untill soft but not falling apart. Drain off potatoes and let steam evaporate. Once evaporated lay
          potatoes on
          baking tray and evenly cover with oil. Bake for 18 minutes at 200c / 400f turning halfway through (remember
          potatoes are already cooked we just want to "crispen"
          the edges) done! </p>
        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Bruce</h6>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-evenly;" >
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;" >
            <a href="">➕</a>
            <p>0</p>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;" >
            <a href="">➖</a>
            <p>0</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>